ed="T" n="0841b20"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0841b20"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>江陵府<persName key="A012750">些些</persName>傳（<persName key="A012752">食油師</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0841b21"/><persName key="A012750">釋些些師</persName>，又名<persName key="A012750">青者</persName>，蓋是不與人交狎，口<lb
ed="T" n="0841b22"/>自言些些，故號之矣。<date from-iso="+0780-02-15" key="j20059942015139" to-iso="+0805-02-28">德宗朝</date>，於<placeName key="PL000000027764">渚宮</placeName>游，衣<lb
ed="T" n="0841b23"/>服零<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz9"/>落<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz9"/>，狀極憨癡，而善歌《河滿子》<ptr target="#n1892"/>。縱肆所<lb
ed="T" n="0841b24"/>為，故無定檢。甞遇醉<persName key="A019452">伍伯</persName>，<persName key="A019452">伯</persName>於塗中辱<lb
ed="T" n="0841b25"/>之，抑令唱歌。<persName key="A012750">些</persName>便揚音揭調，詞中皆<anchor xml:id="beg0841001"/>訐<anchor xml:id="end0841001"/><lb
ed="T" n="0841b26"/><persName key="A019452">伍伯</persName>從前陰私惡迹，人所未聞事。<persName key="A019452">伍伯</persName>慚<lb
ed="T" n="0841b27"/>惶，旁聽之者知是聖僧，拜跪悔過焉。<date notBefore-iso="+0785-02-18" key="j20078242009652" notAfter-iso="+0790-02-20"><name>貞元</name><lb
ed="T" n="0841b28"/>初</date>，多入市肆，聚群小隨逐，<placeName key="PL000000023022">楚</placeName>人以興笑本<lb
ed="T" n="0841b29"/>矣。後不測其終。次有<persName key="A012752">僧</persName>憨狂，遊行無度。每<pb ed="T" n="0841c" xml:id="T50.2061.0841c"/><lb
ed="T" n="0841c01"/>斷中<ptr target="#n1893"/>，唯食麻油幾升。如見巨器盛施之，則<lb
ed="T" n="0841c02"/>喜。<placeName key="PL000000027770">荊</placeName><placeName key="PL000000027764">渚</placeName>一家特召啜麻膏，是日又在<placeName key="PL000000028622">湖南</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0841c03"/>齋，分身應供號<persName key="A012752">食油師</persName>焉。</p>
    <p xml:id="pT50p0841c0401"><lb
ed="T" n="0841c04"/>系曰：<persName key="A012750">些</persName>之聲為商為羽耶？通曰：「傳家<anchor xml:id="begd1e36213"/>采<anchor xml:id="endd1e36213"/>錄，<lb
ed="T" n="0841c05"/>其例有二：一則按文不音，二則口授知韻。<lb
ed="T" n="0841c06"/>今得<persName key="A012750"><anchor xml:id="beg0841002"/>些<anchor xml:id="end0841002"/></persName>者，按文也。若<placeName key="PL000000023022">楚</placeName>詞聲餘則蘇箇切<lb
ed="T" n="0841c07"/>也，若山東言少，則寫邪切焉。此師<placeName key="PL000000023022">荊楚</placeName>間事<lb
ed="T" n="0841c08"/>也，其二音以聽來教，<persName key="A012750">些</persName>名同鳥獸之自呼<lb
ed="T" n="0841c09"/>也。</p>
